OL,3,C'There's no one coming through':
OL,4,CButcher shortage impacting Guernsey's
OL,5,Cfarmers
OL,7,FThe Farmers Association say a shortage
OL,8,Fof butchers on the island is causing
OL,9,Fconcern for the industry.
OL,11,FMichael Bray, who heads the
OL,12,Fassociation, says a shortage of
OL,13,Fbutchers means fewer people farm
OL,14,Fanimals such as pigs.
OL,16,FPrime cuts fetch higher prices but
OL,17,Fincreasingly local meat ends up as
OL,18,Fmince. As a result, the profit an
OL,19,Findividual cow can produce are reduced.
