OL,3,C'There's no one coming through':
OL,4,CButcher shortage impacting Guernsey's
OL,5,Cfarmers
OL,7,FTen years ago, Guernsey's abattoir
OL,8,Fused to deal with around 500 animals a
OL,9,Fyear. Now, it's just over 400.
OL,11,FSteve Robert, owner of Cobo Butchers,
OL,12,Fhas been butchering meat for more than
OL,13,F50 years and says butchery is a dying
OL,14,Ftrade: "There's nobody coming through
OL,15,Fnow.
OL,17,F"It's very hands on and very manual
OL,18,Fwork - and people don't tend to like
OL,19,Fthat nowadays.
