OL,7,F"Most of the time they want to go into
OL,8,Fbanking or something else".
OL,10,FSteve's son Richard will take up the
OL,11,Ftrade - but at a time when food
OL,12,Fsecurity and low food miles are
OL,13,Fincreasingly important, more are
OL,14,Fneeded to ensure the industry's future.
